### 로그인 [실패]  - 값이 없이 들어왔을때.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "1111"
}

### 로그인 [실패]  - 값이 없이 들어왔을때.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### 로그인 [실패] 1. 비밀번호가 틀렸을때.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "carami",
  "password": "22"
}


### 로그인 [성공] 2. 정상로그인(토큰발급)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "carami",
  "password": "1111"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
%}




